name: Solana Deads
description: Solana Deads ($DEADS) is the central utility and rewards token of the Solana Deads ecosystem. It powers multiple interconnected products including NFT staking, Death Draw raffle/auction mechanics, Soulbound Gatekeeper wallet-gating, and future GameFi integrations. Designed on SPL Token-2022 with protocol-level extensions, DEADS enforces a sell-side fee router (1.11%) that redistributes to the community treasury, stakers, and ecosystem growth. Token holders and NFT owners alike benefit from enhanced staking yields, governance participation, and access to premium features within the Solana Deads suite of tools and games.
